What happened?

10
00:01:33,890 --> 00:01:35,386
Nothing.

11
00:01:35,851 --> 00:01:37,781
Nothing, really.

12
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:47,580
A bite is stuck in my throat.

13
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:51,640
When one's son is nowhere to be seen,

14
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:56,386
One can't digest the sorrow or the food, Reverend.

15
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:03,820
Nor can I, like you,

16
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:07,196
Defeat grief with sheer will.

17
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:40,346
Did you offer your prayers?

18
00:03:41,596 --> 00:03:44,267
Did you offer your prayers?

19
00:03:44,367 --> 00:03:45,666
Prayers?

20
00:03:45,666 --> 00:03:49,419
It protects you from upheavals and wards off countless troubles, you blighter!

21
00:03:49,419 --> 00:03:50,376
Get up!

22
00:03:50,376 --> 00:03:51,640
Purify yourself right now,

23
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:54,187
And get yourselves on the prayer mat.

24
00:03:54,187 --> 00:03:56,257
Why did you slap me?

25
00:03:56,257 --> 00:03:59,186
Girls like you are only brought to their senses when slapped!

26
00:03:59,186 --> 00:04:00,330
Offer your prayers, quick!

27
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:02,206
And pray for the well-being of those

28
00:04:02,206 --> 00:04:03,787
Whom you meet,

29
00:04:03,787 --> 00:04:05,178
Or call.

30
00:04:05,178 --> 00:04:06,758
What?

31
00:04:07,717 --> 00:04:09,948
While praying today,

32
00:04:09,948 --> 00:04:12,254
My eyes teared up.

33
00:04:12,254 --> 00:04:16,020
I didn't even realise I was weeping!

34
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,907
The angels would be laughing at you right now.

35
00:04:17,907 --> 00:04:19,951
Bother about your own -

36
00:04:19,951 --> 00:04:23,100
They listen either to the clinking of your anklets or the sweet melodies of 'I've tasted blood'!

37
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:26,046
The poor fellows would be sitting with their ears shut!

38
00:04:26,046 --> 00:04:26,822
Get up!

39
00:04:26,822 --> 00:04:28,037
Offer your prayers,

40
00:04:28,037 --> 00:04:31,272
So that it relieves the angel on your left shoulder [scribe noting evil deeds].

41
00:04:31,272 --> 00:04:33,853
I've heard that when your type finally sits on the prayer mat,

42
00:04:33,853 --> 00:04:36,607
One can hope for an immediate relief!

43
00:04:36,607 --> 00:04:38,747
I don't know why my heart's saying

44
00:04:38,747 --> 00:04:42,658
That you're in need of urgent relief.

45
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:43,628
Are you getting up,

46
00:04:43,628 --> 00:04:45,277
Or do you want another?

47
00:04:45,277 --> 00:04:46,908
I am.

48
00:04:48,878 --> 00:04:50,231
Wait.

49
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:52,053
Just for now,

50
00:04:52,053 --> 00:04:53,693
Take off these anklets for a change.

51
00:04:53,693 --> 00:04:58,104
You don't need this background music in orison!

52
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:03,070
You hag!

53
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:25,674
Both the bullets had hit him on the leg, right?

54
00:05:25,674 --> 00:05:26,721
Right...

55
00:05:26,721 --> 00:05:29,916
Then there's nothing to worry about.

56
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,806
Right...

57
00:05:33,921 --> 00:05:36,137
Why aren't the doctors coming out, then?

58
00:05:36,137 --> 00:05:39,048
Why don't they say that everything's fine?

59
00:05:39,048 --> 00:05:41,040
They're busy with the surgery, mun.

60
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,176
Right...

61
00:05:42,176 --> 00:05:43,913
