142
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,440
Why are you scared?

143
00:12:30,546 --> 00:12:35,127
The 'most excellent one' [Afzal] in the eyes of the two of you,

144
00:12:35,127 --> 00:12:41,227
That rapscallion has disappeared from our sights,

145
00:12:41,227 --> 00:12:46,328
And her megrims give your mother's heart a painful plight.

146
00:12:46,328 --> 00:12:50,199
