149
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:59,371
She gets scared.

150
00:12:59,371 --> 00:13:02,299
But you're scared too.

151
00:13:02,631 --> 00:13:05,214
Out of respect, yes.

152
00:13:05,214 --> 00:13:07,895
I've heard

153
00:13:07,895 --> 00:13:11,030
'Ordinary people should be scared'

154
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:15,649
'When a mother gets scared'.

155
00:13:19,310 --> 00:13:21,170
Alright, Ruqaiyya,

156
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:26,670
I've decided to sleep peacefully until dawn.

157
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:29,180
Stop telling your rosary,

158
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:33,850
And chant a hymn to get me sleepy.

159
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:51,330
He's alright now.

160
00:13:51,330 --> 00:13:52,857
He's talking, isn't he?

161
00:13:52,857 --> 00:13:54,147
He's unconscious right now, sir.

162
00:13:54,147 --> 00:13:56,740
When he'd come to in the morning, he'd be talking, too.

163
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,506
Excuse me.

164
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,912
There! That's all it ever was. He's alright now.

165
00:14:01,912 --> 00:14:03,313
Let's get going, then.

166
00:14:03,313 --> 00:14:04,713
Going?

167
00:14:04,713 --> 00:14:07,473
Call me if you need anything.

168
00:14:07,473 --> 00:14:09,359
You'll get it.

169
00:14:09,359 --> 00:14:10,872
C'mon, now.

170
00:14:10,872 --> 00:14:13,870
