171
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:14,460
Just come!

172
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:20,344
Very bad, Mam! We should be staying here, how -- Mam, how could we just leave?
-Everyone's watching you!

173
00:14:34,810 --> 00:14:36,050
Okay.

174
