228
00:17:35,204 --> 00:17:36,574
Babu Hamid?

229
00:17:36,574 --> 00:17:40,005
That blighter would get him papar [snack] with bread and some rotten lentils!

230
00:17:40,005 --> 00:17:41,625
You'd say it yourself, then,

231
00:17:41,625 --> 00:17:43,760
'They got the bullets out, but couldn't get the lentils out'.

232
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:44,601
C'mon, now,

233
