237
00:17:52,372 --> 00:17:53,557
Hey!

238
00:17:53,557 --> 00:17:55,642
Fear God, Mam!

239
00:17:55,642 --> 00:17:58,717
One feels sorrow even when one's enemies are at the hospital.

240
00:17:58,717 --> 00:18:00,267
Then, he's Afzal.

241
